OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fwith variable cloud and clear spells
OL,7,Ffor many. The odd mist or fog patch is
OL,8,Fpossible in some rural spots.
OL,9,FGenerally a mild night, with light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FStaying fine and dry, with
OL,13,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells
OL,14,Fthroughout the day. Feeling warm in
OL,15,Fthe sunshine, with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
