OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying predominantly dry with
OL,7,Fvariable amounts of cloud and some
OL,8,Fclear or sunny spells. A small chance
OL,9,Fof isolated showers. Some light rain
OL,10,Fpossible later Saturday. Temperatures
OL,11,Fgenerally above average.
